sonグループ\n      - Photosynthetic acclimation of higher plants to growth in fluctuating light environments\n      - Dynamic acclimation of photosynthesis increases plant fitness in changing environments\n      \n  - 雑記\n    - 農業気象学会の支部会発表\n    - スライドの接続でぐだったのが心残り\n    - 「ポスドクだから優秀賞を」、という心配りを感じて申し訳無さが...\n      - 精進しよう\n      \n- 11\n\n  347. [Demarsy et al. 2018; Trend Plant Sci](http://www.cell.com/trends/plant-science/fulltext/S1360-1385(17)30272-8); <FONT color=\"green\">高</FONT>\n    - Coping with ‘Dark Sides of the Sun’ through Photoreceptor Signaling\n    - Geneva, Goldschmidt-Clermontグループ\n    - PSII障害の話\n    - 最近こういうwit系のタイトルおおい\n      - 商売っけのあるジャーナル (CNS, OA系) に多い\n      - たまにならいいけど食傷気味\n  \n- 12\n\n  348. [Takizawa et al. 2007; BBA](http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0005272807001557); 低\n    - The thylakoid proton motive force <i>in vivo</i>. Quantitative, non-invasive probes, energetics, and regulatory consequences of light-induced <i>pmf</i>\n    - Kramer lab\n    \n  349. [Li & Yang 2015; Front Plant Sci](http://journal.frontiersin.org/article/10.3389/fpls.2015.00704/abstract); <FONT color = \"green\">20171212済</FONT>\n    - Advantages of diffuse light for horticultural production and perspectives for further research\n    - D論の抜粋的な温室内の散乱光環境化についてのはなし\n    - そーね、って感じの内容\n\n- 13\n\n  350. [Liesche & Patrick 2017; F1000Research](https://f1000research.com/articles/6-2096); <FONT color = \"green\">低</FONT>\n    - An update on phloem transport: a simple bulk flow under complex regulation\n    - F1000は扱いにやや困る感じだけどとりあえず\n    \n  - 雑記\n    - 忘年会@Rocca\n    \n- 14\n\n  - 雑記\n    - PRIイメージングは個体レベルだとパッケージの構成を結構変えないとダメ臭い\n      - 設計が甘いんだよなぁ...\n      - うーん\n    \n- 15\n\n  351. [Esteban et al. 2017; New Phytol](http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/wol1/doi/10.1111/nph.14932/full); <FONT color=\"blue\">20171215済</FONT>\n    - On the recalcitrant use of Arnon's method for chlorophyll determination\n    - 自分も`Murakami et al. 2014; Plant Biol`ではArnonを使っている\n    